snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP'S LAWYER HITS ON AMBER HEARD'S WITNESS!? Oopsie!🤭😅 | Depp vs Heard Trial funny moments
snippet.description:

When Johnny Depp's lawyer HIT ON Amber Heard's Witness (Dr. Hughes) during a cross-examination of the psychologist or psychiatrist or whatever the heck she does... Watch Johnny Depp's lawyer TOTALLY EMBARRASS HIMSELF!🤭 In this exclusive clip! It's one of the top Depp vs Heard Trial funny moments for sure!
